---
source: tests/cli.rs
expression: "help_output(& [\"setup\", \"--help\"])"
---
Set up a fresh machine with the lab toolchain

Usage: hpds setup [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --profile <PROFILE>  Setup profile: dev (this machine's toolchain) or server (full lab server provisioning; Linux only) [default: dev] [possible values: dev, server]
  -v, --verbose            Show more detail (underlying commands, tool names)
      --plan               Print the numbered plan for the profile and exit without running or prompting
  -q, --quiet              Suppress all output except errors
      --no-color           Disable colored output
  -y, --yes                Skip all prompts: run every step and pre-approve sudo steps
      --config <PATH>      Use this config file instead of discovering hpds.toml
  -h, --help               Print help
